Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.35,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Hello, Kawajiri residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.61,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Huh? No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I see. Well done, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:15.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You protected me from that meddlesome Rohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.87,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Listen, you have the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:19.95,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,So, now that we've covered that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.87,Secondary,Shinobu,0,0,0,,They had the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:28.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...I suppose it's about time I headed to work to keep my wonderful family happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.93,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Before I go, could I give you a goodbye kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.59,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.28,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?! My precious teapot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.53,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,How could you do such an awful thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:57.57,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I have no idea what's gotten into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:00.54,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,You never answer me when I call! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:03.04,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.92,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Mama, he isn't human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:19.68,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I let anyone know anything about him,\N they'll be blown up, and this morning will reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.56,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I keep letting him do whatever he wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:26.44,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...it may not happen right away,\N but eventually he'll kill Mama and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.79,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,K-Kishibe Rohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.58,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's the only person I know other than Kira with an ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.04,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have to do something about Kishibe Rohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:55.26,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Only someone with an ability like Kishibe Rohan's\N stands a chance of defeating Kira and saving Mama and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.31,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-There he is! It's Rohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.56,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I try talking to Rohan, he'll blow up and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.73,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Then this morning will repeat again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.69,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have to let Rohan know about Kira without talking to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.82,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have to change fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.62,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.79,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: [WARNING] Do not read any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.79,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,This is the ability Rohan used on me last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.54,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.30,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm not anywhere near Rohan right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.47,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He hasn't even seen me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:42.89,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Once fate has been set in motion, it can't be stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.02,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...Hayato!
Comment: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:08.51,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:16.94,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(141,890)\fs60}Episode 36: {\fs80} Another One Bites the Dust Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.73,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Damn, the weather forecast didn't say it would rain! {This line is also in episode 35}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:26.12,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You must be under the impression that you \Npurposely broke that teapot earlier, but you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:31.12,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Anything that happened in\N a previous cycle will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.62,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It will because it has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's fated to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:42.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If you were turned into a book during a previous cycle,\N you'll turn into a book again, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:46.43,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That is what makes Killer Queen: Bites the Dust unrivaled. {oh boy here we go}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It erases any evidence of my identity \Nand puts everything else back as it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:58.56,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Which means that before I head off to work, I'll get to witness Rohan being blown to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.90,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: It rained. → At 8:27 AM, lightning struck above the Pepsi sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.90,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't let Rohan die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.11,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't let Rohan be killed by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Ah, poor Kishibe Rohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.89,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:33.14,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Right now, he has no idea he's\N about to meet his utter demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:38.65,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I wonder if he realizes that he'll never\N be able to draw comics ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.46,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,R-Rohan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.47,Main,Reimi,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:19.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hayato, the fact you ever encountered Rohan will soon\N completely disappear, and the morning will continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:26.49,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If I undid Bites the Dust right now, \NRohan's death would become permanent and never repeat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I won't do that for now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.99,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,A few of his friends intend to show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:37.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You're going to automatically defeat them for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Just like an undetectable landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:50.55,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,But don't worry. Bites the Dust won't harm you in any way, \Nso you're free to relax and live your life as a normal young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Well, Papa has to head to the station. {This and the next line are from episode 35}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Study hard and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:04.52,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's all my fault... Because he met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.53,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Because he met me, Kishibe Rohan died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:25.04,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Is there any way I can beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.76,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can I ask you something quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.64,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.35,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I think my watch is busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.60,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Hello? Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.53,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's 8:33...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.90,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? Have I seen you somewhere around town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.91,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.99,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Do I look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.37,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.58,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I see... Guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.54,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking something so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.75,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,So it's 8:33, huh? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.21,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro! It really is past 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,But that's strange... Where did Mr. Rohan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.93,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-These are Kishibe Rohan's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.39,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,They were supposed to meet with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.60,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}He left the car door wide open with the key still in the ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.98,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}This isn't like Mr. Rohan at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.70,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's Mr. Rohan's earring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.81,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,They probably have abilities like he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:26.40,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-They came here to ask me about Kira Yoshikage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:39.70,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Oh no! It will be really bad if they figure out \NI'm Kawajiri Hayato and ask me about my Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Crap, sorry kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I overslept and now I'm late to meet my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.51,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? You look {\i1}real{\i0} familiar...\N Where've I seen ya before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.68,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Ah, Josuke and Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.51,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.64,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yo, Koichi! \NMornin', Mr. Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.81,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}What, so Rohan's the only one not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:11.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll never find Kawajiri Hayato's house since that bastard has the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.73,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-There's two more of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.40,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,When he said his friends were coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.06,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...he must have been talking about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I totally forgot I grabbed this from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Here. Your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.58,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.58,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,His face at this angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:28.08,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Something about this angle... \NI'm sure I've seen him somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:32.09,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Where was it? \NIt must have been {\i1}somewhere{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.84,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Koichi. Look at the name on his backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.09,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Kawajiri Hayato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.85,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.18,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-They found me out!
Comment: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.99,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Kawajiri Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.28,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,What's he doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.91,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.08,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,D-Does this have something to do with\N Mr. Rohan not being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:08.58,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If these guys start asking me about Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.09,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...they'll all get blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.34,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,D-Don't do it! Don't ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:21.35,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If all of you die, then who's gonna beat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.10,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Even if I have to trick them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.52,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...I can't let these guys die, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.27,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:37.28,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me why you were filming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.78,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Why were you recording footage of your da{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.20,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,M-My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.04,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I need a doctor! My nose is gushing blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.62,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-I... Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Your nose is bleeding? Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.84,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I gotta go... Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You don't need to see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.64,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Your nose isn't bleeding anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.35,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.85,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The name's Higashikata Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,, That guy is a relative of mine, Mr. Kujo Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...the guy with the scary face is Nijimura Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...and finally, this friendly-looking guy is Hirose Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You go to Budogaoka Elementary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.29,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're not gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We have just a few questions for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...about this photo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.13,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If you weren't up to anything, then don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:39.05,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-I was up to something! \NDon't ask me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.05,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,You can't ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is this guy in the photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:44.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...your da{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.14,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't say another word!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.90,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.82,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Now they're gonna ask me even more questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.19,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What do you mean "Don't say another word?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.40,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What are we not supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.45,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't stop it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.49,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Are you talking about your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.12,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,They're gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.62,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,They're all gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.04,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,You suddenly shouted "Stop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't say another word?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.50,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,But we ain't asked ya nothin' yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.63,Main,Jojo,0,0,0,,Is it possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:23.38,Main,Jojo,0,0,0,,...that the act of asking you a question is a bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:23.38,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're gonna explode... Explode... Explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.22,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.39,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-If I kill myself, then no one else will have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.90,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Since I'm the bomb, I just need to kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:43.28,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I die, I'm sure these people will be able to\N beat him and save my Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:51.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Come on, just ask him about Kawajiri Kosaku already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.25,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Wait, Josuke. Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What are you bending over for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.76,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.60,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't cut my throat with the box cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.64,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.81,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.23,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ain't no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.60,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.10,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Orara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:24.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,To be more precise,\N it's Killer Queen's tertiary bomb, Bites the Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.32,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Retaliation is futile. {RESISTANCE IS FUTILE YOU WILL BE ASSIMILATED}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:31.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If you can see me, \Nthen I'm already inside your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how many of you \Nthere are, because all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.67,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...you tried discovering my identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:59.06,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Wow, you're already awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:04.57,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I'm happy you finally answered me for once, \Nbut there's no need to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.65,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready, so come eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:18.58,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I couldn't prevent it... \NThe rest of them were attacked, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:23.09,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's no use... No matter how hard I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:28.09,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...in an hour, fate will eliminate those guys, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.05,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't even kill myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:37.18,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,My death would probably be bad for him, \Nso he made Bites the Dust automatically protect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.60,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kira Yoshikage is a complete monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:48.78,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Either he has to die, \Nor he has to undo Bites the Dust for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.20,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...otherwise, those guys will die for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.39,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Either he has to die, or he has to undo Bites the Dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:20.44,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,For as long as I've lived,\N I never thought I would have to kill someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:26.61,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I didn't think an eleven year-old boy like me\N stood a chance of killing a monster like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.61,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,But there's one way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:33.57,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,A way for an eleven-year-old like me to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.12,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:44.29,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,And it's sleeping quietly in the attic, \Nlike a gun resting in an armory...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:50.88,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,For the first time in my life, \NI prayed to God from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:57.22,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,"God, please help me kill this man."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.82,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:16.12,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,The cat-like plant starts moving when sunlight hits it, \Nthen attacks by shooting air bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:20.12,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Even with just a little sunlight in the room, it's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.37,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,This behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:26.50,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can take advantage of this behavior \Nand have it shoot him at point blank range!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.05,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Point blank range...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.38,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,But when can I do it, and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.47,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can't do it anywhere near the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.10,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Mama is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.77,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,That's right, my hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.27,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He'll try to put the hat on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.52,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,That will be my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.65,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'll be at point blank range when he comes up behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.61,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,That's when I have to get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.62,Narrator,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?! You're kidding! We're already on air?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.20,Narrator,News,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, well... It is currently 7:55...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.16,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Papa said he wanted another cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.84,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.42,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No, wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.72,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,The Sakurais don't live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.48,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Here, darling! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.02,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Your freshly brewed cup of coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.70,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's a lovely morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:43.04,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I suppose another cup before work couldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.04,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Fate doesn't change with Bites the Dust, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:52.55,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Something that was destroyed once \Nwill be destroyed again, no matter how much you fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.72,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,That's what you said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.43,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,My precious tea set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.93,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.06,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Okay Mama, I'm going to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:16.24,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'll always be here for you! \NI'll protect you forever, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.00,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:34.84,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,I can never tell what that boy is thinking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.84,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,...maybe he's a good kid after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.10,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry! I'll clean this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.85,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,Not much we can do now that it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.27,Main,Shinobu,0,0,0,,More importantly, were you burnt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.27,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No... I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.74,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's still not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.20,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He's not here... He's still not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:09.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,S-Something's wrong! He should have been here by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.79,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Why isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.54,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Damn, the weather forecast didn't say it would rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.67,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's starting to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.93,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Did leaving the house before him change fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.26,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:28.73,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If he's coming here to put the hat on my head, \Nhe should be approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.23,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,L-Lightning struck the Pepsi sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.82,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down! I have two minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:41.70,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have more than two minutes before\N Kishibe Rohan is automatically blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.41,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have to believe in fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.46,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He's... already standing by the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.21,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's already right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:59.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What a lovely morning, indeed. \NAnd yet, Hayato was acting strangely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:00.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I have a nagging suspicion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:09.98,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,We must have repeated this morning \Nat least... three... no, four times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.98,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-Is he just that smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.48,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.61,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'll have to attack him from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:27.66,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-Is he staying away from me because he knows\N I have the cat plant, and that I could attack him up close?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.75,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No... He's too close to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,But... I still have to defeat him with just one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:43.88,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I miss, Rohan will explode, then he'll undo \NBites the Dust after the rest of them are eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.72,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He'll win if that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.85,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,There's no more time... Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.60,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Move one more step to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:55.98,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If he steps out from behind that dirty-looking tree, I can get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:01.23,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,What?! H-He's hiding himself even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.90,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,The look in Hayato's eyes when he left the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:06.49,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,He seemed awfully determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:12.00,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,He gave me the same look that horrible \NHirose Koichi and that shit stain Josuke did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:16.46,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,My instincts are telling me to cautiously observe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:20.25,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Not that there's much Hayato can do to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.51,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:27.01,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Once it's a few seconds past 8:29, \Nthe attack on Kishibe Rohan will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.27,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,The poor brat is shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:37.48,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,His eyes look like cesspools full of drowning rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.98,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I must have imagined seeing that determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.36,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,His eyes are those of someone who has given up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.86,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I came here to bring you your hat, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.41,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,If there is a God, I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:00.54,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}And I thank fate for making this serial killer \Nmove out from behind the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.80,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I feel a fighting spirit burning inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.26,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Take this, Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:12.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:22.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I hit him dead-on! I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.24,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Kawajiri Hayato isn't coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.32,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,He must have taken a different route to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:35.25,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You're finished, serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:42.67,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.67,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.38,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...with how quickly my nails have been growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:54.93,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...I thought my luck had turned completely rotten, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:56.81,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...I had something in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:01.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My luck finally seems to have \Ntaken a turn for the better since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:07.49,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Remember when Mama's precious\N tea cup shattered this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:15.49,Main,Kra,0,0,0,,{\an8}The coffee spilled and burned my hand and wrist, \Nso I took off my watch and put it inside my chest pocket.
